ction. Fishing Measures makes an invaluable contribution to contemporary debates regarding relationships between capitalism, the environment, and science.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCod fisherieszNewfoundland and LabradorxHistoryy19th century. 0aCod fisherieszNewfoundland and LabradorxHistoryy20th century. 0aScience and statezNewfoundland and LabradorxHistoryy19th century. 0aScience and statezNewfoundland and LabradorxHistoryy20th century. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economic History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311127195808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP w/o University of Toronto Press 2023 eBook Packagez978311143542840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978189472598940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781894725989423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781894725989/original  a978-3-11-127195-8  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-143542-8  ACUP w/o University of Toronto Press 2023 eBook Packageb2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles